b8=A.am("Development of a sound controlled video game to teach music concepts,  support creative expression and spark musical interactions between the community of young music learners.\n                    ",A.a6(a9,a9,a9,a9,a9,a9),a9,a9)
r=A.am("Challenges:",A.a6(a9,a9,a9,a9,a9,B.t),a9,a9)
q=A.am("Lack of feedback and social connection are detrimental for the perseverance of music students that rehearse at home. Music video games based on gamification rules can engage students in practice and connect them with their peers. Although, music video games require either replacing the instrument for a controller, which hinders didactic capacity of the game, or physically connecting the instrument to the computer which negatively impacts interaction and range of freedom and creativity.\n                    ",A.a6(a9,a9,a9,a9,a9,a9),a9,a9)
p=A.am("Process:",A.a6(a9,a9,a9,a9,a9,B.t),a9,a9)
o=A.am("The challenge was into four development milestones. Each milestone will produce a deliverable that can be presented as a finished product and be used as a base for the next iteration of development. \n                    ",A.a6(a9,a9,a9,a9,a9,a9),a9,a9)
